<h3><a name="credits">What are the &quot;OVL Credits&quot; and how to use it?</a></h3>

<p>OVL Credits are virtual currency used for super-easy lessons unlocking. It works the same as 
Facebook Credits if you are familiar with it. Or like PrePaid phones &ndash;
you buy some Credits and then use it on what you need and when you need. 
It doesn't expire in time and there are no monthly costs.  
<% if user_signed_in? %>
All payments and unlocks are listed in <%= link_to (t("users.nav.hub"), hub_user_path(current_user))%>.
Buy some OVL Creidts using Credit Card or PayPay in <%= link_to(t("users.nav.credits"), credits_user_path(current_user)) %> section.
<% else %>
All payments and unlocks are listed in Your Hub.
<strong><%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path %></strong> to buy some OVL Credits
<% end %>
and start learning today!
</p>

<p>If you have any questions &ndash; please <a href="#contact">contact us</a>.</p>


