<h2>For Teachers</h2>

<p>You can <strong>earn money by sharing your knowledge in global scale</strong>.</p>

<p>We offer <strong>video production</strong>, <strong>global promotion</strong> and <strong>comision from all forms of distribution</strong>.</p>

OVL has a innovative business model where <strong>you focus only on scenarios of your lessons and interactions with your learners</strong>.
We bare all the costs &ndash; video production, distribution, promotion &ndash; to guarantee the highest quality
and to reach millions of people worldwide.</p>

