<h3>Can you produce videos on your own?</h3>

<p>Yes. As you see in the table above, in this case you earn bigger comision but all video production costs are on your side.
Obviously, you have to meet all quality standards related to content and technical issues.</p>

<h3>Can you publish existed videos recorded for other sites, conferences etc?</h3>

<p>Rather not. We would like to have all the content uniqe, prepared especially for the OVL community.</p>

<h3>Who are we looking for?</h3>

<p>We are looking for passionate and experienced experts who want to earn by sharing their knowledge.</p>

<p>If you have an idea for your own lessons &ndash; please <a href="#contact">contact us by filling an application</a>.</p>

