<h3>What are the requirements?</h3>

<ul>
<li><strong>Great Content</strong> <span class="star">*</span> &ndash; content is the king, period &ndash; enlight us with your knowledge!</li>
<li><strong>Passion</strong> &ndash; show us your love for what you learn and for &quot;Become who you want to be&quot; vision.</li>
<li><strong>Experience</strong> &ndash; tell us about your experience in your topic and in teaching others.</li>
</ul>

<p>
<span class="star">*</span> Every lesson must have specific topic &ndash; "Battle of Britain" rather then "World War II".<br />
<span class="star">*</span> Duration of every video should be from 10 to 30 minutes.<br />
<span class="star">*</span> You should spend at least 10 hours to create detailed script of each lesson.<br />
<span class="star">*</span> Each lesson should have extra materials such as images, links etc.<br />
<span class="star">*</span> You can do from 1 to 10 lessons &ndash; only things you are the best.
</p>

