<h3><a name="work">Work with us!</a></h3>

<p>We are looking for:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Promotion Manager</strong>: responsible for increasing traffic to OVL through social media 
like Facebook and Twitter and traditional media like TV and press. You should be expierienced and ready for full-time work 
in our office in Poznan, Poland.</li>
<li><strong>Translator</strong>: responsible for creating transcripts and captions for
all of our videos. You should know Polish and English fluently. You can work part-time from home.</li>
<li><strong>Mentor / Business Advisor</strong>: we offer shares for advice and connecting with influentials who 
would like to invest in OVL and help to grow it internationally. Passion for education very welcome.</li>
</ul>

